{"tid":1580993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷搭黨鐵] 入嚟睇下黨鐵2018年盈利分佈，點樣可以令佢收皮","createTime":"2019-09-19T10:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:08.000Z","uid":18074,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"edc5a8461ea63fb7e45ba90efa788f6815ea55b5","tid":1580993,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"今日去睇下黨鐵2018年業績報告：<br />\n<br />\n全年佢賺咗<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">126億</span></strong>經常性營利 (EBIT, 未計利息同稅，同埋賣樓收入），其中<br />\n<br />\n1）<span style=\"font-size: large;\">19億（16%）</span>係鐵路營運<br />\n2）<span style=\"font-size: large;\">50億（40%）</span>係地鐵站裡面的商舖租金同站內的廣告<br />\n3）<span style=\"font-size: large;\">42億（34%）</span>係黨鐵商場租金<br />\n4）<span style=\"font-size: large;\">15億（12%）</span>係大陸同外國生意<br />\n<br />\n咁好喇，我地連燈仔可以點發揮影響力呢？<br />\n<br />\n首先，亦係最重要，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷搭</span></span>，直接影響（1）的收入，同時間接會影響埋（2）。地鐵站少咗人，商舖自然叫黨鐵減租，同埋廣告都落少幾個<br />\n<br />\n二，好似<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">cctvb</span></span>咁，直接同商戶反映叫佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好喺黨鐵落廣告</span></span>，亦可考慮杯葛長期喺黨鐵落廣告的商戶<br />\n<br />\n三，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買</span></span>- <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">任何地鐵站內同地鐵商場都一律不消費</span></strong>。黨鐵商場包括德福，青衣城，圓方，等佢地感受下零售寒冬<br />\n<br />\n最後，注意租金係會滯後。通常租約簽3年，唔會即時減到租，所以呢個係長期戰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要黨鐵賺少咗錢，派少咗息，班股東自然嘈佢。同時，作為大股東的政府，收入亦會少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6f0273b67de99a6c1382552014dc3bfc6b87f6","tid":1580993,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5TcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=b86fcccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1c320765b99a30fd38dc2531dfd2a37a942677ae","tid":1580993,"uid":245078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f5de36bbf4bfc11c964c1b94d71e305dc0a7ac4","tid":1580993,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0b8594faf736bb91177997f26adc8f41c4f5646b","tid":1580993,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7f26d3c65a78ba53382d3037ee47b91476d9d9d3","tid":1580993,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"8b8cf7d977b810269a45c0c460703d74ff462746","tid":1580993,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e75a02812b6ecc62df37ba19c0e15581d8997a","tid":1580993,"uid":321374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"1對我黎講好難<br />\n2同3 721已經開始實行<br />\n4唔關我事"},{"pid":"05a7e8d84fc28f9305d878c2bc975013bf9210f0","tid":1580993,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8949e779248434eb18bf2f4d4afbcca5e9ef9468","tid":1580993,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:38:00.00